components.description:
To have your custom components be checked as DOM elements, you can
provide a mapping of your component names to the DOM element name.

Example:

```json
{
"settings": {
"jsx-a11y": {
"components": {
"Link": "a",
"IconButton": "button"
}
}
}
}
```

