OxlintSettings.description:
Configure the behavior of linter plugins.

Here's an example if you're using Next.js in a monorepo:

```json
{
"settings": {
"next": {
"rootDir": "apps/dashboard/"
},
"react": {
"linkComponents": [
{ "name": "Link", "linkAttribute": "to" }
]
},
"jsx-a11y": {
"components": {
"Link": "a",
"Button": "button"
}
}
}
}
```

